"Maps old formatter brace position settings for type declarations to new settings for record declarations.":
org.eclipse.jdt.core.formatter.DefaultCodeFormatterConstants.FORMATTER_BRACE_POSITION_FOR_TYPE_DECLARATION :: sourceVersionGE(14)
=> org.eclipse.jdt.core.formatter.DefaultCodeFormatterConstants.FORMATTER_BRACE_POSITION_FOR_RECORD_DECLARATION
;;

